In order to [flood](strategy) the market with open organizations, we're building a
[product](https://gratipay.com/) to help companies fund the open source
software they depend on. Below are the projects we've got going on right now.
Links are to GitHub projects, milestones, and issues. Dive in!


## Product

1. Finish cleaning up from the Gratipocalypse:
   1. [Decouple](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/milestone/22) ([IG](https://github.com/gratipay/inside.gratipay.com/milestone/9))
   2. [Finish Team Basics](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/milestone/18)
   3. [Pivot](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/milestone/13)
2. Knock pay-what-you-want out of the park:
   1. [Make Widgets 2.0](https://github.com/gratipay/grtp.co/milestone/2)
   2. [Tighten Onboarding Flow](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/milestone/3)
   3. [Solve Corporate Sponsorship of Open-Source](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/milestone/19)
3. Knock take-what-you-want out of the park:
   1. [Implement an AML Program](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/milestone/15)
   2. [Expand Take-What-You-Want Beyond Gratipay](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/issues/3433)


